    <item>
      <title>乐观的中国贸易数据推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四油价保持稳定，在乐观的中国贸易数据以及美国数据显示原油库存增幅小于预期以及燃料库存大幅减少后，维持隔夜涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>防务报告称，中国加强灰色地带战以消耗台湾资源</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾国防部周四的一份报告称，中国加强了针对台湾的灰色地带战，旨在让这个民主岛屿周围的地区充满气球、无人机和民用船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着日本央行即将转向支点的猜测升温，日元上涨；美元贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-falls-with-treasury-yields-views-looming-us-rate-cuts-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元汇率周四触及一个月高位，因市场越来越多地猜测日本央行可能在本月结束负利率，而美国可能在年中降息的押注打压美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-falls-with-treasury-yields-views-looming-us-rate-cuts-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:21:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济不景气，更多中国女性选择单身</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-women-choosing-singledom-economy-stutters-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自由撰稿人柴婉柔认为婚姻是一种不公平的制度。和中国许多年轻女性一样，她是一场不断发展的运动的一部分，该运动设想了一个没有丈夫和孩子的未来，这给政府带来了一个本来可以不做的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-women-choosing-singledom-economy-stutters-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
